  "slides": [
    {
      "id": "slide-deck02-01",
      "presentationId": "presentation-day-1-deck-02",
      "sortOrder": 1,
      "title": "Slide 1",
      "body": "",
      "speakerNotes": "The greatest entrepreneurs never succeed alone.\nPause.\nThey have mentors.\nPause.\nThey have partners.\nPause.\nThey have teammates.\nPause.\nThey have technology that helps them think better.\nPause.\nSPIKE gives you all four.",
      "discussionQuestions": [],
      "imageUrl": "/content/segment-1/week-1/day-1/deck-02/slide-01.png"
    },
    {
      "id": "slide-deck02-02",
      "presentationId": "presentation-day-1-deck-02",
      "sortOrder": 2,
      "title": "Slide 2",
      "body": "",
      "speakerNotes": "One thing you'll notice throughout SPIKE is that we don't use AI to think for you.\n(Pause.)\nWe use AI to help you think better.\nContinue\nThe ideas...\nThe dreams...\nThe purpose...\nThe mission...\nThe venture...\nThey all come from you.\n(Pause.)\nAI simply helps you sharpen them.\nPoint to the Laptop\nImagine you're writing your Purpose Statement.\nYou already know what you want to say.\nBut maybe you're not sure if it's inspiring enough.\nOr clear enough.\nOr specific enough.\nPoint to the AI Suggestions\nInstead of giving you the answer...\nSPIKE asks better questions.\n\"Can you make this clearer?\"\n\"Can you compare different approaches?\"\n\"Can you strengthen your impact?\"\n\"Can you think bigger?\"\nThe Philosophy\nThat's how entrepreneurs grow.\nNot because somebody gives them answers...\nbut because somebody asks better questions.\n(Pause.)\nIn SPIKE...\nAI becomes that thinking partner.\nConnect to Mentors\nAnd that's exactly what your mentors will do as well.\nThe AI helps you think.\nYour squad helps you explore.\nYour mentors help you challenge your assumptions.\nTogether, they make your ideas stronger.\nBring it Back to the Audience\nBy the end of this week...\nyour Venture Blueprint won't be something AI created.\n(Pause.)\nIt will be something you created—\nrefined by AI,\nstrengthened by your squad,\nchallenged by your mentor,\nand inspired by your own purpose.\nTransition\nSo let's begin with the very first question every entrepreneur must answer.\n(Pause.)\nWhy do you want to build this venture?\nThen transition directly into the Venture Blueprint live demonstration",
      "discussionQuestions": [],
      "imageUrl": "/content/segment-1/week-1/day-1/deck-02/slide-02.png"
    },
    {
      "id": "slide-deck02-03",
      "presentationId": "presentation-day-1-deck-02",
      "sortOrder": 3,
      "title": "Slide 3",
      "body": "",
      "speakerNotes": "We will be using this tool.",
      "discussionQuestions": [],
      "imageUrl": "/content/segment-1/week-1/day-1/deck-02/slide-03.png"
    },
    {
      "id": "slide-deck02-04",
      "presentationId": "presentation-day-1-deck-02",
      "sortOrder": 4,
      "title": "Slide 4",
      "body": "",
      "speakerNotes": "Finish your Squad Charter",
      "discussionQuestions": [],
      "imageUrl": "/content/segment-1/week-1/day-1/deck-02/slide-04.png"
    },
    {
      "id": "slide-deck02-05",
      "presentationId": "presentation-day-1-deck-02",
      "sortOrder": 5,
      "title": "Slide 5",
      "body": "",
      "speakerNotes": "Speaker: This will be your Venture Blueprint.\n\"By the end of today, every one of you will have your own Venture Blueprint.”",
      "discussionQuestions": [],
      "imageUrl": "/content/segment-1/week-1/day-1/deck-02/slide-05.png"
    },
    {
      "id": "slide-deck02-06",
      "presentationId": "presentation-day-1-deck-02",
      "sortOrder": 6,
      "title": "Slide 6",
      "body": "",
      "speakerNotes": "Today, we're going to build all of these.",
      "discussionQuestions": [],
      "imageUrl": "/content/segment-1/week-1/day-1/deck-02/slide-06.png"
    },
    {
      "id": "slide-deck02-07",
      "presentationId": "presentation-day-1-deck-02",
      "sortOrder": 7,
      "title": "Slide 7",
      "body": "",
      "speakerNotes": "Your Purpose\n\"You've just refined your ambition.\"\n(Pause.)\n\"Now we're going one level deeper.\"\n\"Ambition answers the question: What do I want to achieve?\"\n(Pause.)\n\"Purpose answers a different question.\"\n(Pause.)\n\"Why does this venture deserve to exist?\"\n\"A successful venture isn't built around a product.\"\n\"It begins with a problem worth solving and people worth serving.\"\n\"Don't worry about writing the perfect purpose statement today.\"\n\"We're still building Version 1.\"\n\"Think about someone whose life becomes better because your venture exists.\"\n(Pause.)\n\"If your venture disappeared tomorrow...\"\n\"Who would miss it?\"\n(Pause.)\n\"And why?\"\n\"Open your Venture Blueprint.\"\n\"Navigate to Purpose.\"\n\"You have twenty minutes.\"\n\"Start building.",
      "discussionQuestions": [],
      "imageUrl": "/content/segment-1/week-1/day-1/deck-02/slide-07.png"
    },
    {
      "id": "slide-deck02-08",
      "presentationId": "presentation-day-1-deck-02",
      "sortOrder": 8,
      "title": "Slide 8",
      "body": "",
      "speakerNotes": "Instead of giving them answers, walk around the room asking questions like:\n\"Who are you trying to help?\"\n\"What frustrates them today?\"\n\"Why does this matter to you personally?\"\n\"If you could solve only one problem, what would it be?\"\n\"Why should anyone care that your venture exists?\"\nTransition to the Next Slide (Share)\nAs the timer ends:\n\"Your first draft doesn't have to be perfect.\"\n\"Now let's see how your Squad can make it stronger.\"\n\"Turn to your Squad.\"",
      "discussionQuestions": [],
      "imageUrl": "/content/segment-1/week-1/day-1/deck-02/slide-08.png"
    },
    {
      "id": "slide-deck02-09",
      "presentationId": "presentation-day-1-deck-02",
      "sortOrder": 9,
      "title": "Slide 9",
      "body": "",
      "speakerNotes": "Prompt\nImagine your life five years from now.\nWhere are you?\nWho are you helping?\nWhat does success look like?\nLarge inspirational image.\n20 minutes.",
      "discussionQuestions": [],
      "imageUrl": "/content/segment-1/week-1/day-1/deck-02/slide-09.png"
    },
